      "output": "\r\n\r\nName          : Intel(R) HD Graphics 630\r\nAdapterRAM    : 1073741824\r\nDriverVersion : 31.0.101.2140\r\nDriverDate    : 05/11/2025 00:00:00\r\n\r\nName          : NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050\r\nAdapterRAM    : 2147483648\r\nDriverVersion : 31.0.15.3179\r\nDriverDate    : 25/04/2023 01:00:00\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
