      "output": "\r\nBankLabel   Capacity Speed Manufacturer\r\n---------   -------- ----- ------------\r\nBANK 0    8589934592  2400 SK Hynix    \r\nBANK 2    8589934592  2400 Samsung     \r\n\r\n\r\n",
      "status": "success",
