    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user has:\n- HP OMEN15-ce0xx laptop\n- Intel Core i5-7300HQ (7th gen, 4C/4T)\n- 16GB DDR4 2400MHz (mixed SK Hynix + Samsung - not ideal but common)\n- NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050\n- Intel HD 630\n\nWHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR on this specific model is a VERY well-known issue. It's related to:\n1. Intel CPU microcode bug affecting7th gen CPUs\n2. CPU power delivery/voltage regulation issues\n3. Motherboard degradation (especially on HP OMEN15-ce0xx)\n\nLet me check more details about the system.",
      "timestamp": 1783146346961
    },
    {
