      "output": "\r\n\r\nModel         : HGST HTS721010A9E630\r\nSize          : 1000202273280\r\nMediaType     : Fixed hard disk media\r\nInterfaceType : IDE\r\n\r\nModel         : ADATA SX6000NP\r\nSize          : 512105932800\r\nMediaType     : Fixed hard disk media\r\nInterfaceType : SCSI\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
